{"tid":922401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【獵人的慈悲】狩獵季未到 小鹿困冰湖3小時獲獵人救走","createTime":"2018-11-30T10:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T11:18:50.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9e3f75942bc3b3f385a66853117307fbbe6d31e5","tid":922401,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T10:37:11.000Z","msg":"獵人原來也有惻隱之心。美國有位獵人見到一隻雄鹿在冰湖上跌跌撞撞無法站起，決定出手救牠而非等牠死亡撿屍。<br />\n<br />\n事發在上周六早上，當時距狩獵季還有2天。賓夕凡尼亞州格里利湖（Greeley Lake）一隻雄鹿被困在離岸約100米的冰湖上。據報牠被困至少3小時，多次嘗試站起來都失敗，後腳因找不到着力點無法撐起。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獵人戴維斯（Josh Davis）見到牠苦苦掙扎心有不忍，決定出手協助。他先登上小船靠近雄鹿，再用繩套住牠的角，後由友人將船拖回岸邊。<br />\n<br />\n戴維斯表示雄鹿上岸後，很快就站起來逃入叢林，「我不想看到牠受苦。我是個獵人，人道地狩獵動物與任由牠在冰上死亡，是有很大的差別的。」賓州狩獵委員會亦讚揚他出手救鹿。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181130&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58974937\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181130%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58974937&d=xbL%2BtSzMZHnQbIUZIGsyPgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=71c59504\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181130%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58974937&h=8416352d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181130&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58974937</a>"},{"pid":"fa97eb95a0c8c0df054fe3208a2e6d4f62f911fd","tid":922401,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T10:38:23.000Z","msg":"過多兩日就&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef892add788f1f160a659be8433ad10ceca546c","tid":922401,"uid":121146,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"賓州狩獵委員會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e829b551fbd0dbc8cdce46570c310aab913e10","tid":922401,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fef892add788f1f160a659be8433ad10ceca546c","tid":922401,"uid":121146,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"賓州狩獵委員會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T10:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08eb3f232b97d78c64c790ddd1e892b0b3c7d761","tid":922401,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fef892add788f1f160a659be8433ad10ceca546c","tid":922401,"uid":121146,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"賓州狩獵委員會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T10:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狩獵搖擺賓州"},{"pid":"6f414cda02ee199baac7c4b80b5590d9bef606ee","tid":922401,"uid":69614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T10:45:42.000Z","msg":"佢做獵人應該係享受過程多於結果"},{"pid":"f91474af9ac72c5b2553757fe460e525a55e7b88","tid":922401,"uid":85431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T10:56:32.000Z","msg":"除非確保自己槍槍爆頭，否則同人道仲有好遠距離，直接認自己心血來潮算啦"},{"pid":"e3613b28fb6cd71a79a2f7a191ae46217efa0c2e","tid":922401,"uid":97389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"加拿大有法例規定喺狩獵季節, 都唔可以獵殺太年輕的獵物.<br />\n美國應該都有類似的法例, 唔係獵人慈悲, 只係法例規管佐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過救獵物脫險就真係為佐享受過程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7481a5fe81c66e075650ece15118e65c2a614a","tid":922401,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T11:18:50.000Z","msg":"Red Dead Redemption 2"}]}